    "summary": "Engineer, designer, and storyteller, I am driven by a profound commitment to pioneering change through my PhD research. My focus lies in exploring narratives, bottom-up innovation, and user-driven solutions that foster a more inclusive future. With a deep-rooted passion for sustainability, I believe that asking different questions is essential to uncovering fresh perspectives and novel answers.\n\nHaving worked extensively in India, utilizing media, and emergent technology platforms for education, problem-solving, and community participation, I have witnessed firsthand the transformative power of narratives and bottom-up approaches. I bring a wealth of experience from collaborating with diverse communities, tackling complex socio-technical systems, and championing user innovation.\n\nIn my quest for a PhD, I am dedicated to unraveling the intricate relationship between narratives, bottom-up innovation, and sustainable alternatives.\n\nBy leveraging my expertise in engineering and design, I strive to contribute to a paradigm shift that embraces user-driven solutions, challenges the status quo, and fosters inclusivity. I firmly believe that collectively, we can pave the way for a brighter tomorrow.\n\nLet's connect to explore opportunities for collaboration, delve into the transformative power of narratives, unravel the complexities of bottom-up innovation, and together, forge a path toward a more inclusive future.",
